敢唔理poly手足處於主動位 我地就偏要反其道而行 要佢地估我地下一步係乜 <br />\n<br />\n你地可能話如果攻入去點算 但其實大家明知班狗要攻我地可以做嘅只有好少 倒不如爭取時間 記住我地係要做主動嗰個<br />\n<br />\n港島手足你地好重要 政府機關睇你地點玩 <br />\n<br />\n我知而加好多人出左去改變唔到d咩 我講呢d唔係想撥冷水 我只係希望捱到聽日大家可以改玩法 當然最好係今日救到手足 唔想再失去任何一人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:10:24.000Z","msg":"咪就係咁囉 叫啲人唔好去poly又比人屌"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"感情用事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPoly根本狗唔會攻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"攻咗咁點?"},{"pid":"e4eb4c0be1fd3f9428de30b2205a575d5abe9e13","tid":1734574,"uid":39436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdfb287d5fb9d43022e43fbaa203e501a48838cb","tid":1734574,"uid":15084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b295d27a91538dcee8613c65348be27b1958d148","tid":1734574,"uid":39436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52f0ce4ee9b655bd887a5daed8a9584f53231ec8","tid":1734574,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"Poly手足可能仲想人攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"所以我唔會怪，鬧任何一個手足 只會分析，勸導"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"大家都有唔同睇法<br />\n其實點解唔可以why not both？開花+反圍poly<br />\n當然你會話人手問題，但同樣地呢樣就係考驗緊呢場運動命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:34:05.000Z","msg":"最好當然係咁 但當唔夠人嘅時候就要分配人手"},{"pid":"eec219a76338751a5216958ce3532744b9252ba8","tid":1734574,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:34:32.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"aabf0a59e5ac957839bf60fa364b8a59da3aeaae","tid":1734574,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a67169eed80f24e0ea9688bd0e3d1138ae1edfb2","tid":1734574,"uid":10125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e39399d50be880f55b8eced1a3378f2a522c926","tid":1734574,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"